OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772554283
OL,3,CTeenager arrested following stabbing
OL,4,Cin park
OL,6,FA 17-year-old boy has been arrested
OL,7,Ffollowing a stabbing in Victoria Park
OL,8,Fin Worthing.
OL,10,FPolice were called to the park at
OL,11,Faround 2:45am on Saturday 28 February,
OL,12,Ffollowing reports a man had sustained
OL,13,Fserious injuries.
OL,15,FOfficers believe the stabbing happened
OL,16,Fafter a brief interaction between the
OL,17,Fvictim, a man who is in his 40s, and
OL,18,Ftwo others.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
