PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772554283
OL,3,CTeenager arrested following stabbing
OL,4,Cin park
OL,6,FThey are described as wearing all grey
OL,7,Ftracksuits with hoods up and faces
OL,8,Fcovered.
OL,10,FFollowing the incident the victim has
OL,11,Fbeen discharged from hospital and
OL,12,Fcontinues to recover at home.
OL,14,FOn Sunday, 1 March, the boy, from
OL,15,FBrighton, was arrested on suspicion of
OL,16,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,17,Fintent, and with being concerned in
OL,18,Fthe supply of a Class A drug. He
OL,19,Fremains in custody.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
