PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772554283
OL,3,CTeenager arrested following stabbing
OL,4,Cin park
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant, Harry Mansbridge
OL,7,Fsaid: "A team are working hard to
OL,8,Fprogress a series of enquiries,
OL,9,Fincluding the collection of CCTV that
OL,10,Fcould be vital to the investigation.
OL,12,F"Following our earlier appeal, we
OL,13,Fwould like to thank everyone who has
OL,14,Fcome forward with information so far.
OL,15,FWe continue to urge anyone who
OL,16,Fbelieves they may be able to assist us
OL,17,Fto make a report."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/3
